d reduces violence. Her results advance research and policy on peacebuilding and democracy promotion in new and surprising ways.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aDemocratizationzDeveloping countries. 0aElection monitoringzDeveloping countries. 0aElectionszDeveloping countries. 0aPolitical violencezDeveloping countries. 4aInternational Studies. 4aPolitical Science & Political History. 4aPublic Policy.  aincrease or reduce violence.  ainternational democracy aid.  ainternational election support.  apeacebuilding and deomcracy promotion.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065198008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics, Law & Social Sciences 2019 ENGz978311061013008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2019z9783110606485oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150173655140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501736551423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501736551/original  a978-3-11-061013-0  EBOOK PACKAGE Economics, Law & Social Sciences 2019 ENGb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-065198-0  Cornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DSWb2019